<s> If the source html contains a tag with an uppercase attribute, how can it be  </s>
<s> converted to lowercase?  </s>
<s> The uppercase value is not valid XHTML.  </s>
<s> E.g. on http://www.apache.org/index.html the form tag contains the method with a uppercase value: It is maybe not a feature of tidy to turn this to lowercase?  </s>
